                    border: hasDueWarning
                        ? Border.all(color: dueStatusColor, width: 1.5)
                        : null,
                  ),
                  child: Row(
                    children: [
                      Container(
                        width: 24,
                        height: 24,
                        decoration: BoxDecoration(
                          color: hasDueWarning ? Colors.white : Colors.black12,
                          borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(4),
                        ),
                        child: Center(
                          child: Text(
                            '${widget.taskNumber}',
                            style: TextStyle(
